column2:
So heres the thing;
This game is unique in it's experience because it is ALSO a puzzle. I think the safe-house checkpoint system is one of a kind. 

And heres why I love it;
This has been and will always live in my heart as my favorite game. When this came out in 2009, my mom bought it. As a young gal' I loved zombie related anything. I played this game for 7 years straight at least once a week, until I graduated high school. I still play this when time allows because it's a great game.

Used to be a really fun game, still is real fun if you play with your friends;

Otherwise, the remaining "community" is insanely rude and I don't think I went a single match where someone wasn't an ass, a single match through ALL 5 CHAPTERS (4 or 5? HAH! Everybody's left), or someone doesn't vote kick someone for a mistake that, let's be face it, is regular and expectable in multiplayer games? 

Iunno, used to love this game, now I can't even play it and have fun it seems

My brother and I gave ourselves nightmares playing this at a tender age;
I can continue to give myself nightmares as an adult.

10/10

The second part of the game is much more detailed in every detail.
 Added in the second part:
 - more gaming companies;
 - a lot of firearms and hand-to-hand weapons;
 - adrenaline and a defibrillator were added to the first-aid kit and pills (with which you can bring a dead comrade back to life);
 - added new special infected;
 - also added grenade launcher and machine gun M60, whose ammunition cannot be replenished;
 - "Fat Man's Vomit" has been added to thrown weapons, which, when broken, attracts a large horde of infected;
 - Four new game modes have also been added: Realism, Gathering, Mutations and Combat: Realism.
 Also, new achievements have been added that can be earned on the added game modes.
 GENERAL IMPRESSION:
 Better than the first part of the game can only be the second

Zombie killing simulator, but;
Throw some mods up in this b*tch and you've got

Scooby Doo: The Gang Has Had Enough. Follow the cast of Mystery Inc. as they finally rid the earth of the monsters that once plagued them in their past. They will put a stop to this nightmare, and they will let nobody stand in their way.
